info.html_description:
Introduction

This is the “policy” product for the public portal of the Alliance of Glycobiologists for Detection of Cancer and Cancer Risk, or Glycans. This product specifies no custom content types or look-and-feel but instead specifies minimum policy settings and orchestrates all other dependent components. To turn a Plone site into the Glycans site, just install this component.
